    <title>新的开始——开新坑</title>
    <url>/2020/05/20/%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%BC%80%E6%96%B0%E5%9D%91/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>emmm，从想想踏入信息安全圈到慢慢踏入快两年了，不过从最近才开始正式踏入，最近在主学密码学和信息安全概论，开始对信息安全有了最初的正是了解，以前写过我作为学渣眼中的信息安全，觉得自己那时见识浅薄，认为自己能概括好信息安全，到后来才发现这是一门多么严谨、重要的学科，甚至是，不过也有了最初的认识。</p>
<p>因为最近一直在忙，没时间写多少东西，所以一直没有更新博客，这是我0202年的第一篇博客打算立一个flag，开个新坑，打算改一下我自己博客的形式开始更新一些我自己弄的技术文章，一些工具我是怎么开始学习使用的，也会推荐我喜欢看的刊物和博客。</p>
<p>这里分享一个白帽的HipHop（本来想直接在这里分享音乐的但是关于版权问题无法直接分享所以分享一下歌词然后给大家一个链接）</p>
<figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span></span><br><span class="line">歌手：Lil Mark</span><br><span class="line">所属专辑：Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span></span><br><span class="line">作曲 : 无</span><br><span class="line">作词 : Lil Mark/Hacking Club</span><br><span class="line">这里是Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span></span><br><span class="line">from <span class="number">04T</span></span><br><span class="line">有人心里有鬼 还在种木马的腿</span><br><span class="line">一个真正的白帽 从来不会后退</span><br><span class="line">嘲讽完对手 再把奖金拿到手</span><br><span class="line">我们中国的白帽 就要遍布全球</span><br><span class="line">HC儿技术的flow, 正气集与一身</span><br><span class="line">东方白帽实力 要让世界震惊</span><br><span class="line">没有挖不到的洞 只有拿不完的冠军</span><br><span class="line">HC儿的<span class="built_in">style</span> 让我唱给你听</span><br><span class="line">利用子时太炸 让你玩儿了命的 哇</span><br><span class="line">尖叫声太大 一招拿下</span><br><span class="line">好像开了外挂 太海尅没办法</span><br><span class="line">有章有法 从来不说大话</span><br><span class="line">看我三军任命 代码上天入地</span><br><span class="line">看我丹田之气 配着DJ放的Beat</span><br><span class="line">为了技术 每个人都在努力</span><br><span class="line">我们根本就不在乎 所谓的成绩</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Hacking club <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">我们不看ID 只用技术说话</span><br><span class="line">Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">我们志在必得 就是这么强大</span><br><span class="line">Hacking club <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">有朋友有兄弟 有一起的park</span><br><span class="line">Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">一个团结的队伍 <span class="number">04T</span>的家</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这个SQL注入WAF看哥们儿怎么绕</span><br><span class="line">一个简单的策略就想跟我单挑</span><br><span class="line">你是参数污染 还是编码绕过的招</span><br><span class="line">谁的操作最耀 谁的水平最高</span><br><span class="line">一块儿跳一块儿笑一块儿燥一块儿闹</span><br><span class="line">一块跑一块儿吆一块玩儿海尅<span class="built_in">style</span></span><br><span class="line">这个绕过真骚 绕出hacker的<span class="built_in">style</span></span><br><span class="line">来离近点儿 让你感受粉丝的尖叫</span><br><span class="line">（welcome to the <span class="built_in">new</span> world）</span><br><span class="line">这是不一样的味儿</span><br><span class="line">在这只用技术较劲儿,</span><br><span class="line">这是龙待的地儿</span><br><span class="line">别过来闹事儿 给你提一个醒儿</span><br><span class="line">别来这儿犯劲儿 给你留一个印儿</span><br><span class="line">See Hacking来一段</span><br><span class="line">该怎么判断 有漏洞就赚</span><br><span class="line">say <span class="number">5.4</span>. <span class="number">3.2</span><span class="number">.1</span>......</span><br><span class="line">Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">我们来自江湖 用技术打天下</span><br><span class="line">Hacking club <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">我们志在必得 就是这么强大</span><br><span class="line">Hacking <span class="built_in">style</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> hiphop</span><br><span class="line">有信任有原则我们共建这的家</span><br><span class="line">Hacking club <span class="keyword">and</span> Hiphop</span><br><span class="line">有梦想的hacker 执剑走天涯</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
